      "title": "Warrants for Wasantha Mudali and Jinarathana Thera",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage today (21st) issued warrants to the convener of the Inter-University Student Council Wasantha Mudalige and Jinarathana Thero of Rathkarave.",
        "It is due to the fact that they did not appear before the court in a complaint filed by the police alleging that they acted as an unlawful crowd in the year 2021."
      ],
